This is a (multiple allowed):

* [x] bug
* [ ] enhancement
* [ ] feature-discussion (RFC)

* CakePHP Version: 4.1.6
* Platform and Target: nginx, php-fpm, php 7.2, mysql

### What you did
My application attempts to save an entity where not all of the fields configured for translation are saved (i.e. some are set, some are not set). Here is an example test case.
```php
     public function testAllowEmptyFalseWithNull()
    {
        $table = $this->getTableLocator()->get('Articles');
        $table->addBehavior('Translate', ['fields' => ['title', 'description'], 'allowEmptyTranslations' => false]);

        $article = $table->find()->first();
        $this->assertSame(1, $article->get('id'));

        $article = $table->patchEntity($article, [
            '_translations' => [
                'fra' => [
                    'title' => 'Title',
                ],
            ],
        ]);

        $table->save($article);

        // Remove the Behavior to unset the content != '' condition
        $table->removeBehavior('Translate');

        $fra = $table->I18n->find()->where(['locale' => 'fra'])->first();
        $this->assertNotEmpty($fra);
    }
```

### What happened
```
2) Cake\Test\TestCase\ORM\Behavior\TranslateBehaviorTest::testAllowEmptyFalseWithNull
TypeError: strlen() expects parameter 1 to be string, null given

/workspace/cakephp/src/ORM/Behavior/Translate/TranslateStrategyTrait.php:114
/workspace/cakephp/src/ORM/Behavior/Translate/EavStrategy.php:243
/workspace/cakephp/src/ORM/Behavior/TranslateBehavior.php:338
/workspace/cakephp/src/Event/EventManager.php:309
/workspace/cakephp/src/Event/EventManager.php:286
/workspace/cakephp/src/Event/EventDispatcherTrait.php:92
/workspace/cakephp/src/ORM/Table.php:1936
/workspace/cakephp/src/ORM/Table.php:1870
/workspace/cakephp/src/ORM/Table.php:1559
/workspace/cakephp/src/Database/Connection.php:691
/workspace/cakephp/src/ORM/Table.php:1560
/workspace/cakephp/src/ORM/Table.php:1871
/workspace/cakephp/tests/TestCase/ORM/Behavior/TranslateBehaviorTest.php:997
```

I believe this issue was introduced in c24dd3a37d5365a58accfb67f2ef772268d410ea when `declare(strict_types=1);` was added to `src/ORM/Behavior/Translate/TranslateStrategyTrait.php`

### What you expected to happen
Test passes
